data.text:
The Serbian actor Lazar Ristovski these days he is enjoying an exotic trip with his 39 years younger girlfriend Anica Lazic.

Lazar Ristovski and Anica Lazic traveled together to the Maldives, and the actress shared a joint photo on her Instagram profile.

In the photo, the two emerge from the water together in bathing suits and hold hands.

"When he leads, I don't ask where," Anita wrote in the description of the photo.

Let's recall, Anica Lazic recently revealed whether she fantasized about her wedding as a girl.

- I did not fantasize about getting married when I was a girl, even today it is very important to me. I see it more as a form, and the essence is more important to me. We women love to wear wedding dresses. I'm not suffering to get married, it's more important for me to live the essence of love, and I already have that, thank God - said Anica.

Their love met with numerous condemnations, Anica met with great condemnations, but she clearly and loudly stood behind the love. As she says, the negative comments made her even stronger.

- I made a promise to myself that I will be brave in love, I don't allow myself to be a coward and I always do what my heart demands - she said in the show "Premiere".
